The '''Anzat language''' was the language used by the [[Anzat (species)|Anzat]] [[Species/Legends|species]]. The language was apparently an archaic one, only known by the Anzati, who also used [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]] when dealing with other people in [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]]. Its written form was so old that there were no known samples anywhere in the galaxy.

